Find the derivative of \(f(x)=x^2\) at x=3

exp_1 <- expression(x^2)
deriv_1 <- deriv(exp_1, "x")
deriv_1
## expression({
##     .value <- x^2
##     .grad <- array(0, c(length(.value), 1L), list(NULL, c("x")))
##     .grad[, "x"] <- 2 * x
##     attr(.value, "gradient") <- .grad
##     .value
## })
x <- 3
eval(deriv_1)
## [1] 9
## attr(,"gradient")
##      x
## [1,] 6

Find the derivative of \(P(a)=2(3a+2)^45\) at a=1.2

exp_2 <- expression(2 * (3 * a + 2)^4 - 5)
deriv_2 <- deriv(exp_2, "a")
deriv_2
## expression({
##     .expr2 <- 3 * a + 2
##     .value <- 2 * .expr2^4 - 5
##     .grad <- array(0, c(length(.value), 1L), list(NULL, c("a")))
##     .grad[, "a"] <- 2 * (4 * (3 * .expr2^3))
##     attr(.value, "gradient") <- .grad
##     .value
## })
a <- 1.2
eval(deriv_2)
## [1] 1961.899
## attr(,"gradient")
##             a
## [1,] 4214.784

Find the derivative of \(g(t)=4t/(t^2+1)^3\) at t=0

exp_3 <- expression(-4 * t /(t^2 + 1)^ 3)
deriv_3 <- deriv(exp_3, "t")
deriv_3
## expression({
##     .expr2 <- -4 * t
##     .expr4 <- t^2 + 1
##     .expr5 <- .expr4^3
##     .value <- .expr2/.expr5
##     .grad <- array(0, c(length(.value), 1L), list(NULL, c("t")))
##     .grad[, "t"] <- -(4/.expr5 + .expr2 * (3 * (2 * t * .expr4^2))/.expr5^2)
##     attr(.value, "gradient") <- .grad
##     .value
## })
t <- 0
eval(deriv_3)
## [1] 0
## attr(,"gradient")
##       t
## [1,] -4
